title: Roasted Eggplant Bengal Curry with Basmati Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: There’s something decadent about the eggplant, especially when roasted so this Bengal curry will feel like a special treat. Add
more veggies to the eggplant and cook them with punchy mustard seeds. The fluffy rice will melt in your mouth as you dig into
this curry. We’ll see you at the bottom of the bowl!

